{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "莱姬希（Fes限定Ver.） 第2话 失落的技术",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唉，说是要找线索，\\n结果这里净是些\\n看不懂的书啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "算了吧，莱姬希。太危险了。\\n——拒绝。绝对不会有事的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嗯？你们在干什么呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120187_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "哇！什、什么东西！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——看起来是麦斯特罗制造的魔导兵器。\\n——还能用战斗人偶的指令来驱动。\\n很方便。带走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120187_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "带回去！？倒是可以，但！？\\n喂，莱姬希，快阻止他啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "了解。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——啊……闯祸了呢。\\n——这次只是没控制好而已。\\n下次就好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "真是的，书架上的书\\n都散了一地……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这本书……\\n写着“战斗人偶开发记录”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "给我看看。\\n——快看看里面的内容！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "怎么样？有什么线索吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以部分肯定。我一个个说。\\n首先根据记录上所说，\\n所谓战斗人偶……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "是重现了700年前的\\n古代文明技术的魔导兵器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "700年前啊。等等，\\n你们被造出来是在300年前吧。\\n那再往前推700年……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——就是1000年前呢。\\n正好是第一次封魔战争时期。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "第一次封魔战争！？战斗人偶\\n原来是个神话级别的技术吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "看来是这样没错。\\n但神话级别的技术\\n似乎不止战斗人偶这一个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——从书中可以得知，\\n我的体内还有另一种\\n古代文明的技术结晶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "还有一种？\\n那是什么样的技术呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——是卢卡也见过的东西。\\n从自然界采集魔力并将其\\n物质化的装置……“魔幻炉”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那是之前在黎布湖\\n看到的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "魔幻炉——采集魔力\\n并将其实体化加以利用的\\n古代智慧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "听起来就不是什么好东西啊……\\n体内藏着那种东西，\\n你们的身体不会有事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "嗯，并没有那么大的规模，\\n应该不足以对周围\\n造成什么危害。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那就好……但为什么\\n你体内会有魔幻炉呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——卢卡难得问了个好问题啊。\\n这与伊甸园模式有关。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂，莱姬希……\\n你说“难得”是什么意思……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "就是字面上的意思。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你、你这家伙……唉，算了。\\n那跟伊甸园模式有什么关系呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "魔幻炉与伊甸园模式本身\\n息息相关。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "通过启动魔幻炉\\n来提高各个回路\\n对周围魔力的吸收效率……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "最终使身体各处的信息处理能力\\n和反应速度产生质的飞越——\\n这就是伊甸园模式。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "呃……虽然太复杂的听不懂，\\n不过伊甸园模式那强大的力量\\n其实是来源于魔幻炉吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以肯定。\\n卢卡难得抓住了要点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "真是谢谢你的夸奖。\\n那么？如此便利的魔幻炉，\\n为什么至今都没有启动呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——这是因为……\\n伊甸园模式的启动上\\n存在着“缺陷”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "缺陷？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "嗯。伊甸园模式通过一次性\\n解除所有限制，将体内全部回路\\n都用于魔幻炉的启动……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "缺陷就在于此。\\n解除限制后，\\n会强制启动另一个模式。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "解除限制……感觉经常能听到\\n莱姬希说这个词啊。\\n那是……啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "没错，是不分敌我\\n进行攻击的杀戮模式。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "解除限制使战斗能力\\n获得巨大提升的同时，\\n无法进行战斗以外的行动……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "换句话说，\\n单凭莱姬希一个人\\n是不可能启动伊甸园模式的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不可能……那上次\\n为什么启动了呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——因为那时马斯古拉的心\\n获得了杀戮模式的控制权。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "在我进入杀戮模式后，\\n可以由马斯古拉\\n来控制我的身体。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——不过，要获得控制权\\n似乎也有条件。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "什么条件？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——那就是……\\n马斯古拉和我的意志\\n完全同步。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——用人类的话来说，\\n应该叫心意相通吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "回想起来的确如此，\\n我正是在那之前下定决心\\n要和莱姬希并肩作战的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "也就是说，那时是因为马斯古拉\\n和莱姬希想要战斗的意志成功同步，\\n才启动了伊甸园模式吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "嗯。虽然还有些在意的地方……\\n但遗憾的是，从书上得知的信息\\n就只有这些了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "诶！？最关键的让伊甸园模式\\n稳定下来的方法呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——没有记载。甚至没有提到\\n为什么会造成如此大的负荷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "可恶……明明只差一点了！\\n那除此之外呢？\\n还有没有什么其它线索……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "是谁在那边！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01",
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔帝国军长官",
            "context": "唔……战斗人偶！？\\n你们是阿尔贝里亚的人！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "啧！被发现了……\\n我们走，开溜！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "了解。\\n——明白！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100032_04_01_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}